<h1>Karolina Krzyżanowska's homepage</h1>

<p>Welcome to my homepage. I am a PhD student at the
Department of Theoretical Philosophy, Faculty of Philosophy,
University of Groningen. I am affiliated with the <a
 href="http://formalphilosophy.org">Formal Epistemology Project</a>.
I am studying under the supervision of <a href="#">Igor Douven</a>.

I received my
Master's degree in the Institute of Philosophy at the University of
Warsaw in 2009. My master's thesis on belief reports from linguistic
and cognitive perspective was supervised by Justyna Grudzińska.

at the Centre for Logic
and Analytical Philosophy at the University of Leuven, working in
the <a href="http://formalphilosophy.org">Formal Epistemology
Project</a>. My supervisor
is <a href="https://perswww.kuleuven.be/~u0015782/">Igor Douven</a>. I
graduated in philosophy at
the <a href="http://www.uw.edu.pl/en/">University of Warsaw</a> in
2009 with a MA thesis being on belief reports in linguistic and
cognitive perspective. I am currently working on beliefs revision and
sematics of subjunctive conditionals.</p>

